<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="candidate-accepted.css" />
    <title>Application Accepted</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <header class="email-header">
        <h1>Congratulations, <%= first_name %>!</h1>
      </header>
      <main>
        <p>We are excited to inform you that your application for the position of <strong><%= job_title %></strong> has been <strong>accepted</strong>.</p>
        <p>You are now advancing to the next stage of our selection process. A member of our team will contact you shortly to discuss the next steps, which may include an interview or additional assessments.</p>
        <p>We appreciate your enthusiasm and interest in joining us, and we look forward to learning more about you in the upcoming stages!</p>
      </main>
      <footer class="email-footer">
        <p>Thank you,<br />The Job Finder Team</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
